description: Chrome Cookin’ is roamin’ through Brooklyn, and serving up their crazy-tasty take on home cooking. This cool crew offers a scrumptious selection of breakfast, burgers, salads, and other perfect munches on their yummy menu, which includes Bacon, Egg, & Cheese Sandwiches, Grilled Cheese with American, Swiss, and Brie, and the L.J. Grilled Turkey Burger, American cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, onion, slaw, sunny-side up egg, jalapeños, chrome roasted aioli, all heaped on a toasted potato bun. If you’re craving all this and more, come on out to Chrome Cookin’ and find just what your appetite is looking for.
name: Chrome Cookin'
